body:
The following query searches for the movies between the years
`2010` and `2015` in the `movies` collection. The query
requests a total count of the results:

```json
db.movies.aggregate([
  {
    "$searchMeta": {
      "range": {
        "path": "year",
        "gte": 2010,
        "lte": 2015
      },
      "count": {
        "type": "total"
      }
    }
  }
])
```

MongoDB Search returns the following results:

```json
{ "count" : { "total" : NumberLong(5971) } }
```

To learn more about the results, see [Count Results](count-results).
